  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nA recent change for https://crbug.com/chromium/1113558 updated the way in which access checks are performed when a frame attached to the debugger is navigated. Previously, checks would only be run against the frame itself; now, checks are run against subframes as well."
